WEBVTT

00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:13.559
I remember you loved hibiscus cakes the most as a child.

00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:15.600
I specifically asked the Bureau of Imperial Cuisine to make some.

00:01:15.759 --> 00:01:16.839
I also instructed them

00:01:16.839 --> 00:01:18.639
to use freshly ground glutinous rice flour.

00:01:19.039 --> 00:01:19.879
Taste it.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.719
See if it still tastes as you remember.

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:30.719
A tongue worn by five years of northern frontier sand

00:01:31.480 --> 00:01:32.960
can no longer taste such sweetness.

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:34.840
The people and matters in this palace...

00:01:35.320 --> 00:01:37.239
have they not also changed beyond recognition?

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:40.480
A Xuan.

00:01:40.840 --> 00:01:43.239
I know your grief over Eldest Sister's passing is hard to quell.

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:45.400
Although you and His Majesty have known each other since childhood,

00:01:45.599 --> 00:01:48.040
you must not be rude to him again as you were today.

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:49.520
Noble Consort, you exaggerate.

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:51.999
I have always strictly observed the etiquette between ruler and subject.

00:01:52.120 --> 00:01:53.120
When was I rude?

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:54.559
A Xuan.

00:01:55.080 --> 00:01:56.800
Must you be so distant with me?

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:57.599
I am your Second Sister.

00:01:57.599 --> 00:01:59.400
Eldest Sister passed away only a few days ago,

00:01:59.599 --> 00:02:01.120
and Second Sister has already been promoted to Noble Consort.

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:03.040
Now you even hold the Seal of the Phoenix in her stead.

00:02:03.440 --> 00:02:04.440
Do you think, Second Sister,

00:02:04.679 --> 00:02:06.040
that I should congratulate you?

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:10.559
So you do not truly intend to treat my health.

00:02:10.959 --> 00:02:13.040
I am merely your excuse to stay in the palace.

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:16.639
Within these palace walls,

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:18.240
amidst fine clothes and rich food,

00:02:18.480 --> 00:02:21.400
the Noble Consort can rise step by step under Eldest Sister's shadow.

00:02:21.760 --> 00:02:23.439
If I use Your Highness to seek a future,

00:02:23.639 --> 00:02:24.960
I presume you would not mind.

00:02:43.480 --> 00:02:44.159
No.

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:48.079
Not this one either.

00:02:50.919 --> 00:02:51.600
No.

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:58.159
Almost all the incense sticks commonly used in the palace

00:02:58.719 --> 00:02:59.960
are here.

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:01.960
It seems that knockout incense

00:03:02.439 --> 00:03:03.680
most likely came from outside the palace.

00:03:04.359 --> 00:03:05.840
If it is an item from outside,

00:03:06.079 --> 00:03:07.639
where should I even begin to investigate?

00:03:36.600 --> 00:03:37.799
Seven days before the fire,

00:03:38.079 --> 00:03:40.160
the record of collecting ice silkworm silk was torn out.

00:03:40.399 --> 00:03:41.200
As expected.

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:42.560
That great fire

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:43.839
was caused by someone intentionally.

00:03:43.839 --> 00:03:45.679
Everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire, stand in the courtyard

00:03:45.679 --> 00:03:46.600
and await questioning.

00:03:58.119 --> 00:03:59.880
This Directress Li of the Bureau of Palace Affairs

00:03:59.880 --> 00:04:01.239
is a living King of Hell.

00:04:01.359 --> 00:04:02.440
She specializes in interrogations,

00:04:02.639 --> 00:04:04.079
and her methods are terrifying.

00:04:04.519 --> 00:04:06.760
I act on the orders of Noble Consort Meng

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.959
to thoroughly investigate the case of the Nine-Phoenix and Pheasant Pattern.

00:04:09.679 --> 00:04:11.399
Until the true culprit is found,

00:04:11.839 --> 00:04:14.359
the gates of the Bureau of Imperial Attire shall not open.

00:04:14.799 --> 00:04:16.000
Food, clothing, shelter, and transportation

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:17.880
will all be taken over by the Bureau of Palace Affairs.

00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:20.679
I have plenty of patience.

00:04:24.239 --> 00:04:25.720
It seems Manager Chen's death

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:27.440
did not make Noble Consort Meng give up.

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:30.160
If that is the case,

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:31.760
I fear we won't be able to leave for days.

00:04:32.399 --> 00:04:33.600
This is a huge trouble.

00:04:34.200 --> 00:04:36.519
Enter the records room in pairs for questioning.

00:04:36.639 --> 00:04:37.799
Informants will be rewarded.

00:04:37.799 --> 00:04:39.839
Those who conceal information will share the guilt.

00:04:46.480 --> 00:04:47.399
I saw it.

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:49.639
You killed Eunuch Sun.

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:55.040
Next group.

00:05:13.919 --> 00:05:15.359
Seize the palace maid Feng Qing.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:20.560
It's actually her.

00:05:21.519 --> 00:05:22.600
Palace maid Feng Qing.

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:24.160
Do you know your crime?

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:25.880
This slave does not know what crime she has committed.

00:05:26.079 --> 00:05:27.360
Please explain, My Lady.

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:30.000
Someone reported that you returned late last night.

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:31.560
Acting suspiciously.

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:32.839
Where did you go?

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:35.719
Were you secretly sketching the Pheasant Pattern?

00:05:36.039 --> 00:05:37.000
My Lady, please perceive the truth.

00:05:37.279 --> 00:05:39.320
This slave went to prepare silk threads last night.

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.440
That is why I returned late.

00:05:48.039 --> 00:05:49.639
How did you get the injuries on your hands?

00:05:49.839 --> 00:05:51.599
You embroidered the Nine-Phoenix and Pheasant Pattern.

00:05:51.719 --> 00:05:52.639
My Lady, please perceive the truth.

00:05:52.880 --> 00:05:55.399
The Nine-Phoenix and Pheasant Pattern requires superb skill.

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:57.399
Embroidery patterns are only possessed by past Managers...

00:05:57.399 --> 00:05:58.719
...and the Director of the Imperial Wardrobe.

00:05:58.719 --> 00:05:59.920
How would this slave know of it?

00:06:00.479 --> 00:06:01.920
If this slave possessed such skill,

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.399
how could I prick my hands like this?

00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:07.440
Returning late yesterday...

00:06:07.639 --> 00:06:08.839
...and having injuries on your hands.

00:06:09.320 --> 00:06:11.079
Could it be that these are all coincidences?

00:06:11.719 --> 00:06:12.479
Torture her.

00:06:20.079 --> 00:06:20.920
Spare my life, My Lady!

00:06:21.320 --> 00:06:22.360
Spare my life, My Lady!

00:06:23.159 --> 00:06:24.880
I really overestimated her before.

00:06:25.079 --> 00:06:25.880
This calamity...

00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:27.680
...I fear she cannot escape it.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:28.959
Spare my life, My Lady!

00:06:29.279 --> 00:06:30.120
This slave confesses!

00:06:30.360 --> 00:06:31.159
This slave confesses!

00:06:34.680 --> 00:06:35.719
This slave is clumsy.

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:36.800
My embroidery skills are poor.

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:38.760
I was reprimanded by the Manager.

00:06:39.079 --> 00:06:40.240
Even Eunuch Sun...

00:06:41.039 --> 00:06:43.959
...Eunuch Sun also punished this slave for this matter.

00:06:44.039 --> 00:06:45.880
That is why this slave practiced embroidery every night.

00:06:45.880 --> 00:06:46.959
I did not speak of it...

00:06:47.079 --> 00:06:48.560
...only because I feared being clumsy...

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:49.920
...and being kicked out of the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

00:06:50.279 --> 00:06:51.240
Eunuch Sun?

00:06:52.279 --> 00:06:53.440
Someone from the Directorate of Ceremonial.

00:06:53.839 --> 00:06:54.599
Reporting, My Lady.

00:06:54.839 --> 00:06:57.159
Eunuch Sun was previously Director of the Imperial Wardrobe.

00:06:57.839 --> 00:06:58.959
In that case...

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:02.639
...he would also know the Nine-Phoenix and Pheasant Pattern.

00:07:06.320 --> 00:07:09.320
Follow me to search Eunuch Sun's room.

00:07:12.760 --> 00:07:13.519
Let's go.

00:07:19.760 --> 00:07:21.560
So she intentionally showed a weakness...

00:07:21.760 --> 00:07:22.839
...to shift the blame.

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:24.039
Quite clever.

00:07:24.920 --> 00:07:26.599
It seems I will be able to get away soon too.

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:36.240
Directress.

00:07:36.719 --> 00:07:38.200
We have not yet found Eunuch Sun.

00:07:38.320 --> 00:07:39.639
But... but this...

00:07:47.399 --> 00:07:48.039
Gu Qing.

00:07:48.519 --> 00:07:49.519
Late Empress.

00:07:56.479 --> 00:07:59.159
Eunuch Sun, your death is well-deserved.

00:07:59.399 --> 00:08:01.479
You make a perfect scapegoat for This Palace.

00:08:08.039 --> 00:08:09.920
It indeed comes from the same hand.

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:11.839
My Lady, please perceive the truth.

00:08:12.039 --> 00:08:14.599
Then this slave can be considered innocent.

00:08:17.479 --> 00:08:19.599
My Lady, Eunuch Sun has been found.

00:08:19.719 --> 00:08:21.680
Found... found his corpse.

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:22.320
Stop.

00:08:24.320 --> 00:08:26.800
The body was discovered so quickly.

00:08:28.880 --> 00:08:30.079
You come with me.

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:32.240
Identify the body.

00:08:33.039 --> 00:08:33.719
Yes.

00:08:37.639 --> 00:08:39.079
It smells so bad. It's terrifying.

00:08:39.279 --> 00:08:40.200
Reporting to Directress.

00:08:40.519 --> 00:08:41.880
This morning, palace servants cleaned the Cold Palace...

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:43.200
...and smelled a stench coming from the well.

00:08:43.279 --> 00:08:44.440
That is how the body was discovered.

00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:46.639
Judging by the official robes, it should be Eunuch Sun.

00:08:58.920 --> 00:09:00.599
When you went to deliver silk threads last night...

00:09:01.079 --> 00:09:02.639
...did you see Eunuch Sun?

00:09:09.639 --> 00:09:10.839
My Lady, this...

00:09:11.039 --> 00:09:12.639
This looks like some kind of ritual object.

00:09:31.599 --> 00:09:33.680
Eunuch Sun admired the Late Empress

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:35.680
and resented Your Highness leading the Imperial Sericiculture Rite.

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:38.039
So he conspired with Matron Chen

00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:40.360
to embroider the Nine-Phoenix and Pheasant Pattern on the robe.

00:09:40.880 --> 00:09:42.920
He then committed suicide to escape punishment,

00:09:43.759 --> 00:09:45.440
following the Late Empress in death.

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:47.160
Yes.

00:09:47.879 --> 00:09:49.759
This humble official also found

00:09:50.040 --> 00:09:51.520
sacrificial items by the Cold Palace wall.

00:09:51.999 --> 00:09:53.280
It must be that Eunuch Sun,

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.759
knowing he had committed a capital crime,

00:09:54.879 --> 00:09:55.959
after performing the sacrifice,

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:57.680
threw himself into a well and died.

00:09:59.200 --> 00:10:00.839
A filthy eunuch,

00:10:01.239 --> 00:10:03.160
daring to imitate a man's deep affection.

00:10:03.560 --> 00:10:06.119
Should Your Highness report this to Your Majesty?

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.200
Why bother Your Majesty with such a trifle?

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:10.640
It is enough that the matter is clarified.

00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:13.200
Directress Li, you handled this assignment well.

00:10:13.920 --> 00:10:14.719
Reward her.

00:10:15.599 --> 00:10:16.640
Thank you, Your Highness.

00:10:21.320 --> 00:10:22.440
You are truly formidable, my Lady.

00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:24.200
You solved the case in just one day.

00:10:24.879 --> 00:10:26.719
It went a bit too smoothly, though.

00:10:26.959 --> 00:10:28.520
The corpse's face was so rotten;

00:10:28.520 --> 00:10:29.879
even I dared not look at it closely.

00:10:29.879 --> 00:10:31.599
Yet you were able to close the case quickly.

00:10:31.599 --> 00:10:32.599
I admire you.

00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:36.520
Eunuch Sun drew the pheasant pattern last night,

00:10:36.959 --> 00:10:38.320
and died after the sacrifice.

00:10:38.680 --> 00:10:40.320
In just a few short hours,

00:10:40.839 --> 00:10:41.800
how could the corpse's face

00:10:41.959 --> 00:10:43.680
rot beyond recognition?

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:47.800
Arrange for a coroner to examine the body secretly.

00:10:58.719 --> 00:10:59.800
You return to the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

00:10:59.879 --> 00:11:01.280
Secretly check the palace maids' rouge.

00:11:01.959 --> 00:11:03.320
Especially Feng Qing's.

00:11:03.599 --> 00:11:04.359
Yes.

00:11:14.740 --> 00:11:15.299
Feng Qing.

00:11:20.580 --> 00:11:21.940
The scent of this incense...

00:11:22.700 --> 00:11:24.179
is exactly the same as in the mourning hall that day.

00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:29.740
Feng Qing, Feng Qing.

00:11:29.819 --> 00:11:31.500
Wen Xin, what are you doing?

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:33.059
It wasn't me, I didn't do it.

00:11:33.059 --> 00:11:34.179
I didn't report you.

00:11:34.179 --> 00:11:35.859
It wasn't me who reported you, Feng Qing.

00:11:35.859 --> 00:11:36.660
It wasn't me.

00:11:40.859 --> 00:11:41.900
You misunderstood me.

00:11:47.979 --> 00:11:49.620
I saw you kill Eunuch Sun.

00:11:49.819 --> 00:11:51.219
But I didn't tell Directress Li.

00:11:52.859 --> 00:11:54.059
I don't understand what you're saying.

00:11:56.660 --> 00:11:58.979
This was left when Eunuch Sun tortured me.

00:11:59.260 --> 00:12:00.740
If you hadn't killed him,

00:12:01.179 --> 00:12:03.020
I might be the one dead today.

00:12:03.819 --> 00:12:04.579
Feng Qing.

00:12:05.339 --> 00:12:06.059
Thank you.

00:12:10.179 --> 00:12:11.660
To think you suffered such an ordeal.

00:12:17.420 --> 00:12:18.219
What incense is this?

00:12:19.459 --> 00:12:21.099
This is Western Regions Calming Incense.

00:12:21.500 --> 00:12:23.699
Burning it by the bed helps one sleep faster.

00:12:24.179 --> 00:12:25.380
Western Regions Calming Incense.

00:12:26.099 --> 00:12:28.099
How did a Bureau of Imperial Attire maid get this?

00:12:29.260 --> 00:12:30.540
My younger sister, Wen Tang,

00:12:30.540 --> 00:12:32.900
gave it to me when she served in Consort Su's palace.

00:12:37.540 --> 00:12:38.859
Consort Su.

00:12:43.780 --> 00:12:45.740
Can this incense cause dizziness and weakness?

00:12:46.939 --> 00:12:49.699
It does cause some dizziness and weakness if burned for long.

00:12:50.300 --> 00:12:51.020
What's wrong?

00:12:55.020 --> 00:12:56.219
Directress Li.

00:12:57.020 --> 00:12:58.099
Why is she here?

00:12:58.339 --> 00:12:59.900
Has something gone wrong again?

00:13:00.459 --> 00:13:02.859
Feng Qing, where is your rouge?

00:13:12.420 --> 00:13:14.900
Rouge in the palace is issued once a season.

00:13:15.099 --> 00:13:17.819
The Bureau of Imperial Attire's rouge was issued last month.

00:13:18.780 --> 00:13:20.020
None of it has been used much.

00:13:20.339 --> 00:13:21.380
Except for yours.

00:13:23.699 --> 00:13:25.140
My rouge, when I got up at night...

00:13:25.140 --> 00:13:26.380
I accidentally knocked it over.

00:13:26.819 --> 00:13:28.859
Why do you ask about my rouge, My Lady?

00:13:29.699 --> 00:13:30.939
This slave can testify.

00:13:31.339 --> 00:13:34.500
I saw Feng Qing knock over the rouge with my own eyes.

00:13:39.020 --> 00:13:42.219
Are you sure you saw it with your own eyes?

00:13:43.179 --> 00:13:43.819
Yes.

00:13:45.459 --> 00:13:46.939
Testimony alone is not credible.

00:13:47.459 --> 00:13:49.260
It only counts after surviving torture.

00:13:50.140 --> 00:13:51.260
Take Feng Qing away.

00:13:51.540 --> 00:13:52.740
Go back and interrogate her slowly.

00:13:56.620 --> 00:13:57.900
You hinted to me...

00:13:57.979 --> 00:14:00.059
That Eunuch Sun knew how to embroider the pheasant pattern.

00:14:00.300 --> 00:14:01.540
I was also in his room...

00:14:01.540 --> 00:14:03.179
And found an item of the Late Empress.

00:14:03.420 --> 00:14:04.300
Immediately after,

00:14:04.300 --> 00:14:06.059
His body was discovered.

00:14:06.459 --> 00:14:07.540
All of this...

00:14:08.059 --> 00:14:09.699
Went too smoothly.

00:14:10.020 --> 00:14:12.260
Solving cases quickly is your ability, My Lady.

00:14:12.300 --> 00:14:13.500
What does it have to do with this slave?

00:14:13.500 --> 00:14:15.579
The corpse's face was sprinkled with honey.

00:14:15.579 --> 00:14:17.059
That is why, within a few hours,

00:14:17.059 --> 00:14:18.979
It was gnawed beyond recognition by fish and shrimp.

00:14:19.660 --> 00:14:20.819
You did this...

00:14:20.819 --> 00:14:22.900
Simply to destroy traces of the murder.

00:14:23.699 --> 00:14:26.020
But the rouge you broke while killing him...

00:14:26.579 --> 00:14:29.059
Happened to stick to Eunuch Sun's trouser leg.

00:14:29.339 --> 00:14:30.699
What you just said, My Lady...

00:14:30.699 --> 00:14:31.859
Is all speculation.

00:14:33.140 --> 00:14:33.939
It seems...

00:14:34.540 --> 00:14:38.099
You won't tell the truth without torture.

00:14:38.380 --> 00:14:39.699
This slave cannot defend herself.

00:14:40.620 --> 00:14:43.459
But I wonder if you are prepared...

00:14:43.579 --> 00:14:45.059
To admit to Noble Consort Meng...

00:14:45.219 --> 00:14:46.420
That you investigated the truth incorrectly.

00:14:53.699 --> 00:14:55.059
Are you threatening me?

00:14:58.819 --> 00:15:00.740
For me to dispose of a palace maid...

00:15:01.179 --> 00:15:03.179
Is like crushing an ant.

00:15:04.059 --> 00:15:05.420
My death is not worth pitying.

00:15:06.900 --> 00:15:07.979
But a person...

00:15:08.179 --> 00:15:11.020
Who can help you rise to become Shanggong...

00:15:11.219 --> 00:15:13.059
Is surely better than a cold corpse.

00:15:13.300 --> 00:15:14.219
Don't you agree?

00:15:16.819 --> 00:15:17.699
Rely on you?

00:15:18.099 --> 00:15:20.219
Someone who can't even save herself?

00:15:22.260 --> 00:15:24.900
You have stagnated in this position for ten years.

00:15:25.219 --> 00:15:26.260
All because ten years ago...

00:15:26.260 --> 00:15:28.099
You heavily punished the former Chief Eunuch...

00:15:28.140 --> 00:15:29.819
Eunuch Huang's companionship partner.

00:15:30.059 --> 00:15:30.859
Since then,

00:15:30.900 --> 00:15:32.620
You have had no chance for promotion.

00:15:33.420 --> 00:15:35.780
How do you know these palace secrets?

00:15:37.300 --> 00:15:39.660
Who exactly are you?

00:15:40.059 --> 00:15:41.620
Who I am is not important.

00:15:41.900 --> 00:15:44.260
If you believe Eunuch Sun's death...

00:15:44.260 --> 00:15:45.420
Was my doing...

00:15:45.620 --> 00:15:47.660
Since I have the ability to do it seamlessly...

00:15:47.939 --> 00:15:50.140
I am naturally of use to you.

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:53.740
If you are willing to lend me a favorable wind...

00:15:53.979 --> 00:15:56.620
I will surely pave your way to high office.

00:15:57.300 --> 00:15:58.380
An ordinary palace maid...

00:15:58.620 --> 00:16:00.699
How could she have such strategy and spirit?

00:16:01.819 --> 00:16:03.380
Why should I trust you?

00:16:07.339 --> 00:16:09.260
Consort Su of Yongfu Palace.

00:16:09.579 --> 00:16:11.260
I know some of her weaknesses.

00:16:11.380 --> 00:16:13.260
You just need to send me to Yongfu Palace.

00:16:13.540 --> 00:16:14.540
Within three months,

00:16:14.900 --> 00:16:16.260
I will definitely help you...

00:16:17.380 --> 00:16:18.699
Achieve another merit.

00:16:26.219 --> 00:16:27.339
With your appearance...

00:16:28.099 --> 00:16:30.540
